NK041(di)012:1: // rab gnas dge legs 'dod 'jo'i yon bdag bsgo ba'i gtong thun nyer mkho bzhugs so //
NK041(di)012:3: rab tu gnas pa'i mtha' rgyas kyi cho ga las
NK041(di)012:4: yon bdag bsgo ba'i mtshams sbyor gyi bshad pa cung
NK041(di)012:6: thog mar dkon mchog gsum gyi shis brjod kyi tshigs
NK041(di)012:7: bcad sogs 'brel chags kyi bshad pa ci rigs sngon
NK041(di)012:8: du gtong ba'am / med kyang rung ba las /
NK041(di)012:9: de yang 'di ltar spyin pa'i bdag pos lhag pa'i
NK041(di)012:10: bsam pa dang sbyor ba rnam par dag pas bde
NK041(di)012:11: bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten phun sum
NK041(di)012:12: tshogs par bsgrubs nas rab tu gnas par gsol ba
NK041(di)012:13: 'di ni dge legs thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa
NK041(di)012:14: yin te / chos thams cad kyi rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK041(di)012:15: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK041(di)012:16: dkon mchog gsum po ma gtogs pa'i //
NK041(di)012:17: yon gyi gnas 'ga' yod min pas //
NK041(di)012:18: dngos po kun gyis de la mchod //
NK041(di)012:19: ces gsungs pa ltar lha dang bcas pa'i 'gro ba
NK041(di)012:20: mtha' dag gis bsten par bya ba'i bsod nams kyi
NK041(di)012:21: zhing bla na med pa ni dkon mchog rin po
NK041(di)012:22: che rnam pa gsum yin la /
NK041(di)012:23: de yang zab mo'i gnas la blo mchog tu gyur
NK041(di)012:24: pa rnams la ni dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin
NK041(di)012:25: byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye shes rang
NK041(di)012:26: rig pa'i ngo bor ye nas lhun grub tu gnas
NK041(di)012:29: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK041(di)012:30: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK041(di)012:31: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK041(di)012:32: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK041(di)012:35: gang zhig bdag dang sangs rgyas rnams //
NK041(di)012:36: rang bzhin mnyam par rab gnas zhing //
NK041(di)012:37: mi gnas len pa med pa ste //
NK041(di)012:38: de dag bde bar gshegs par 'gyur //
NK041(di)012:39: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK041(di)012:40: rnam par shes dang sems pa rnams //
NK041(di)012:41: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK041(di)012:44: dam pa'i don du 'gro ba yi //
NK041(di)012:45: skyabs ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig yin //
NK041(di)012:46: thub pa chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK041(di)012:48: de lta bu'i don khong du ma chud pa'i gdul
NK041(di)012:49: bya thun mong pa rnams kyi ngor sangs rgyas rnams
NK041(di)012:50: kyi thugs rje'i 'jug pa sku gsung thugs kyi phyag
NK041(di)012:51: rgyar byin gyis brlabs pa rnams tshogs gnyis mngon par
NK041(di)012:52: 'du bya ba'i rten du 'dun bzhag gi dkon mchog
NK041(di)012:53: gsum zhes grags pa la thar 'dod rnams kyis brten
NK041(di)012:54: par bya dgos pa kho na yin la /
NK041(di)012:55: tshul de la dgongs nas dkon mchog gsum gyi rten brten par bcas pa sgrub tshul dang /
NK041(di)012:56: sgrub pa'i phan yon bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig mdo rgyud du mar gsungs pa yin te /
NK041(di)012:58: kun dga' ra ba gtsug lag khang //
NK041(di)012:59: mal stan 'tsho ba nar ma dang //
NK041(di)012:60: zhes sogs rdzas las byung ba'i bsod nams kyi gtso bo yang dge 'dun gyi sde dang /
NK041(di)012:64: mchod rten bzhengs pa rnams yin par gsungs shing /
NK041(di)012:66: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun bye ba phrag du ma
NK041(di)012:67: la lo grangs dpag tu med pa yo byad kyis
NK041(di)012:69: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs tshon gang ba ring
NK041(di)012:70: bsrel gyi snying po can zhig 'jim pa las bsgrub
NK041(di)012:71: pa bsod nams lhag par gsungs pa dang /
NK041(di)012:72: gsal rgyal gyis zhus pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK041(di)012:73: thub pa'i mchod rten byed dam byed bcug pa //
NK041(di)012:74: mya ngan 'joms shing lus kun grims pa dang //
NK041(di)012:75: rin chen mdzod mang 'jig rten gtsor 'gyur zhing //
NK041(di)012:76: mi de dgra yi phyogs las rgyal bar 'gyur //
NK041(di)012:77: bcom ldan 'das kyi mchod rten rnams dang ni //
NK041(di)012:78: sku gzugs rnams la rdul phran ci yod pa //
NK041(di)012:79: de 'dra'i grangs de snyed kyi rgyal srid dang //
NK041(di)012:80: lha yul sa steng mi yis nges par thob //
NK041(di)012:81: gzugs dang gzugs med khams kyi ting 'dzin dang //
NK041(di)012:82: phun sum tshogs pa'i sa mchog kun thob nas //
NK041(di)012:83: tha mar skye dang rga ba la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)012:84: sdug bsngal dang bral sangs rgyas go 'phang thob //
NK041(di)012:87: la las de nyid rin chen sna bdun dang //
NK041(di)012:88: la las de bzhin zangs dang 'khar ba las //
NK041(di)012:89: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi gzugs byas na //
NK041(di)012:90: de dag thams cad byang chub thob par 'gyur //
NK041(di)012:93: sa la sogs la phyag rgyar byas //
NK041(di)012:94: rnam grol rim par thob 'gyur na //
NK041(di)012:95: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK041(di)012:96: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK041(di)012:97: zhes sogs phan yon rgya cher gsungs pa ltar bsgrubs pa'i rten de yang /
NK041(di)012:100: byin gyis brlab pa zhes bya ba'i brdas dge zhing bkra shis par sgrub pa'i cho ga 'di la /
NK041(di)012:102: zhes pas pra ni don lhag por ston pa'i tshig phrad /
NK041(di)012:103: tish+tha ni brtan pa'am yun ring du gnas pa /
NK041(di)012:104: bi d+hi ni cho ga ste rab gnas kyi cho ga 'di nyid kyi dbang du byas na /
NK041(di)012:105: shes byed kyi gzhi bshad pa dang /
NK041(di)012:106: bshad pa'i cho ga ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul gnyis su gnas pa las /
NK041(di)012:113: gang gi tshe bya ba'i dus /
NK041(di)012:116: slob dpon chen pos bde 'dus rab gnas su /
NK041(di)012:117: bya dgos mi dgos gnyis su bstan //
NK041(di)012:119: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gdod ma nas rang
NK041(di)012:120: bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK041(di)012:121: yon tan mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid nam
NK041(di)012:122: mkha' ltar kun khyab tu bzhugs pa'i gnas lugs rtogs
NK041(di)012:123: pa shes rab can gyi dbang du byas nas /
NK041(di)012:125: chos nyid stong pa'i don rtogs na //
NK041(di)012:126: gang zhig gang gis gang du brlab //
NK041(di)012:127: gdod nas ma skyes skye med la //
NK041(di)012:129: chos rnams 'od gsal skye med du //
NK041(di)012:130: rtogs par ldan pas mchod gnas rnams //
NK041(di)012:131: rab tu gnas pa mi dgos so //
NK041(di)012:133: yang sku gzugs kyi rten sogs de bzhin gshegs pa
NK041(di)012:134: rnams kyi thugs rje'i rnam rol sku gsung thugs kyi
NK041(di)012:135: phyag rgyar sprul pa'o snyam pa'i dad pa can gyi
NK041(di)012:136: dbang du byas nas snga ma las /
NK041(di)012:137: yang na stong nyid ma rtogs kyang //
NK041(di)012:138: sku gzugs glegs bam mchod rten sogs //
NK041(di)012:139: sangs rgyas rnam sprul byin brlabs las //
NK041(di)012:140: byung ste min na mi 'byung bar //
NK041(di)012:141: rtogs te shin tu dad ldan na //
NK041(di)012:142: rab tu gnas pa mi dgos so //
NK041(di)012:143: zhes pas de lta bu'i don gnyis po khong du
NK041(di)012:144: ma chud pa'i gdul bya thun mong ba rnams tshogs
NK041(di)012:145: gnyis kyi gnas la 'god pa'i ched du rab gnas
NK041(di)012:146: kyi cho ga dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK041(di)012:147: 'jig rten tha snyad la gnas te //
NK041(di)012:148: kun rdzob don du bstan pa yin //
NK041(di)012:149: zhes drang nges kyi dbye bas gsungs pa bzhin rab gnas kyi rtog pa las kyang /
NK041(di)012:150: sangs rgyas kun na rab tu bzhugs //
NK041(di)012:151: rab tu gnas pa gang yang med //
NK041(di)012:152: 'jig rten kun rdzob la brten nas //
NK041(di)012:153: rab tu gnas pa rab tu btags //
NK041(di)012:156: rten gang la sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK041(di)012:157: rnams bsdus nas dge zhing bkra shis pa'i don can
NK041(di)012:159: khro gnyer can gyi rtog pa las /
NK041(di)012:160: rgyal ba'i sku gzugs bzhengs nas ni //
NK041(di)012:161: gus pas rgyal ba ltar mchod bya //
NK041(di)012:162: thub pas de ltar gzigs nas ni //
NK041(di)012:163: yid can rnams la skyob par mdzad //
NK041(di)012:165: jo bo'i man ngag las kyang /
NK041(di)012:166: rten mthong na yang 'di dag ni //
NK041(di)012:167: byin gyis brlabs las byung ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)012:168: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid yin no //
NK041(di)012:169: snyam du dad cing gus par bya //
NK041(di)012:172: sku gsung thugs kyi rten rnams la //
NK041(di)012:173: ye shes gzhug pa'i byin rlabs can //
NK041(di)012:175: sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid yin //
NK041(di)012:178: su pra tish+tha bi d+hi zhes pa'i sgra las bzang por bsgrub pa dang /
NK041(di)012:179: yun ring du gnas par byed pa'i cho ga ste /
NK041(di)012:180: rten ye shes sems dpa'i ngo bo nyid du bsgrubs pas bzang po dang /
NK041(di)012:181: 'khor ba ji srid du gnas par byed pas yun ring ba'o //
NK041(di)012:182: de gnyis kyang ye shes pa dgug gzhug dang brtan
NK041(di)012:183: bzhugs dang 'brel ba'i phyir rab gnas kyi cho ga
NK041(di)012:188: rten so so'i bdag nyid du gnas pa la yang bgrang rung ngo //
NK041(di)012:190: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs la //
NK041(di)012:191: mtha' yas grol ba'i rgyu yi phyir //
NK041(di)012:192: rgyal ba dgug dang gzhug par bya //
NK041(di)012:194: gnyis pa gang la gnas bya'i rten ni //
NK041(di)012:198: 'bur du byas pa la sogs kyis mtshon pa //
NK041(di)012:199: gzugs sku'i de bzhin gshegs pa zhi khro'i snang brnyan dang /
NK041(di)012:200: gsung gi rten rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang 'phags pa rnams kyi gsung rab glegs bam /
NK041(di)012:201: thugs rten ni chos sku'i rten spyi ming bye brag
NK041(di)012:202: tu btags pa mchod rten brgyad la sogs pa rnams
NK041(di)012:203: dang / gzhan yang gtsug lag khang dang /
NK041(di)012:204: rgyan dang phyag mtshan la sogs pa ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK041(di)012:205: de dag kyang dbyibs dang rgyan la sogs pa so
NK041(di)012:206: so'i mtshan nyid dang ldan par tshad la phebs par
NK041(di)012:208: sku gzugs mtshan nyid ldan pa ste //
NK041(di)012:209: zhi ba la sogs nyams dang ldan //
NK041(di)012:210: tshad kyi tshad la phab cing bzang //
NK041(di)012:211: de 'dra rab tu gnas par bya //
NK041(di)012:213: gsum pa gnas pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK041(di)012:214: skyon yon gyi cha las gnyis te /
NK041(di)012:216: rten de yang rab gnas ma byas pa dang /
NK041(di)012:217: cho ga dman pas byas na'ang mi shis pa dang bsod nams kyi zhing du mi 'gyur te /
NK041(di)012:218: gang du sku gzugs rab rdzogs pa //
NK041(di)012:219: byin ma brlab par ring gnas na //
NK041(di)012:220: de la bkra mi shis pa 'byung //
NK041(di)012:221: de srid mchod par de mi 'os //
NK041(di)012:223: cho ga dman pas mi bya ste //
NK041(di)012:224: rab gnas rtag par bkra mi shis //
NK041(di)012:229: sngar bshad pa'i skyon rnams mi 'byung ba dang /
NK041(di)012:230: rten de nyid mchod pa las bsod nams 'phel zhing
NK041(di)012:231: rgyud byin gyis brlab pa sogs don chen por 'gyur
NK041(di)012:232: ba yin te / de bas 'bad pa thams cad kyis //
NK041(di)012:233: dngos grub 'dod pas nan tan bya //
NK041(di)012:234: cho ga bdag nyid nus pa yis //
NK041(di)012:235: brtag pa las byung tshul legs pas //
NK041(di)012:236: de byas bsod nams che ba ni //
NK041(di)012:237: mthong dang ma mthong rnams su skye //
NK041(di)012:238: sku gzugs sngags kyi mtshan nyid kyis //
NK041(di)012:241: pad+ma dbang chen gyi rgyud las /
NK041(di)012:242: sku gsung thugs rten khyad par phyir //
NK041(di)012:243: rab gnas bzang po'i cho ga bya //
NK041(di)012:245: bzhi pa gnas byed kyi slob dpon ni /
NK041(di)012:246: theg pa gsum gyi bslab pas rgyud sbyangs shing /
NK041(di)012:247: khyad par rdo rje theg pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK041(di)012:248: gis smin cing dam tshig dag pa phyi nang gi
NK041(di)012:249: de nyid bcu sogs slob dpon gyi las rab 'byams
NK041(di)012:251: rab gnas kyi cho ga la mthong brgyud phyin chad
NK041(di)012:252: kyis mkhas pas don mthun du lag tu longs pa
NK041(di)012:253: ste / slob dpon de nyid bcu shes shing //
NK041(di)012:254: mtshan nyid kun dang yang dag ldan //
NK041(di)012:255: phyag rgya sngags dang cho ga shes //
NK041(di)012:256: las rnams kun la mkhas pa'o //
NK041(di)012:260: stangs stabs gdan dang bzlas brjod dang //
NK041(di)012:261: sbyin sreg mchod pa las la sbyar //
NK041(di)012:262: slar bsdu ba yi rnam pa ni //
NK041(di)012:263: phyi yi de nyid bcu yin no //
NK041(di)012:265: phyir bzlog gnyis kyi cho ga dang //
NK041(di)012:266: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK041(di)012:267: kha sbyor dbye ba'i cho ga dang //
NK041(di)012:268: gtor ma rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang //
NK041(di)012:269: drag shul bsgrub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK041(di)012:270: rab tu gnas dang dkyil 'khor sgrub //
NK041(di)012:271: gsang ba'i de nyid bcu yin no //
NK041(di)012:275: khyim na gnas pa rnams rim bzhin rab 'bring tha mar byas pas so //
NK041(di)012:276: lnga pa gang du bya ba'i gnas ni /
NK041(di)012:277: phyogs dang kha dog la sogs pa'i sgo nas zhi rgyas kyi gnas su basngagasa pa dang /
NK041(di)012:278: khyad par bkra shis shing nyams dga' ba'i gnas te /
NK041(di)012:279: yang thog mchod rten la sogs dang //
NK041(di)012:280: khyim dang lha yi gnas rnams su //
NK041(di)012:281: sangs rgyas la sogs rab gnas ni //
NK041(di)012:282: cho ga dag dang ldan par bya //
NK041(di)012:285: bkra shis dag pa chen po'i gnas //
NK041(di)012:286: yid 'ong nyams ni rnam par dga' //
NK041(di)012:287: zhes sogs kyis mtshon te dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rnams las bshad pa bzhin no //
NK041(di)012:288: drug pa gang gi tshe bya ba'i dus ni /
NK041(di)012:289: zla ba drug dang gza' bzhi dang //
NK041(di)012:290: rgyu skar bcu bzhi gang yin dang //
NK041(di)012:291: tshes grangs bdun gyi bdag nyid la //
NK041(di)012:292: rgyal bas rab gnas la sogs basngagasa //
NK041(di)012:293: zhes pa ltar dgun zla tha chung nas dbyar zla
NK041(di)012:294: 'bring po'i bar nyi ma byang bgrod kyi dkar phyogs
NK041(di)012:295: gza' skar 'phrod sbyor bzang zhing bkra shis pa la
NK041(di)012:297: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK041(di)012:298: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK041(di)012:299: byang chub spyod pa cher spyod pas //
NK041(di)012:300: gsang mchog dngos grub myur ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)012:301: gza' skar shis pa blang bar bya //
NK041(di)012:302: zhes pas rig byed kyi gzhung gzhan las kyang shes par bya ba nyid de /
NK041(di)012:304: rig byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK041(di)012:305: dus rnams shes par bya ba ni //
NK041(di)012:306: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK041(di)012:307: 'byor dang dus tshes bzang ba ni //
NK041(di)012:308: mtshan ma'i rtog pa yin mod kyang //
NK041(di)012:309: brtags na bkra shis mtshan ma 'byung //
NK041(di)012:312: dkyil 'khor dang ni rab gnas pa //
NK041(di)012:313: yar gyi ngo la brtag par bya //
NK041(di)012:314: zhes pa'ang gtso che ba'i dbang du dgongs kyi /
NK041(di)012:316: gza' dang skar ma 'dzom gyur na //
NK041(di)012:317: mar gyi ngo la'ang nyes pa med //
NK041(di)012:319: bdun pa gang zhig bya ba'i cho ga ni /
NK041(di)012:320: rten 'brel rab gnas su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)012:322: sangs rgyas sras bcas dad pas spyan drangs nas rten
NK041(di)012:323: la bzhugs su gsol te phyag mchod dang shis brjod
NK041(di)012:324: byed pa mdo lugs su grags pa dang /
NK041(di)012:325: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde tha dad nas gsungs pa rnams dang /
NK041(di)012:326: khyad par rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud mdo sgyu dang
NK041(di)012:327: sgrub sde rnams su gsungs pa'i don pan grub shing
NK041(di)012:328: rta chen por grub pa rnams kyis ji ltar bkral
NK041(di)012:329: ba bzhin snying por dril ba'i cho ga rnam par
NK041(di)012:330: dag pa nyid kyis bya dgos te /
NK041(di)012:331: sangs rgyas la sogs rab gnas ni //
NK041(di)012:332: cho ga dag dang ldan par bya //
NK041(di)012:333: cho ga dman pas mi bya ste //
NK041(di)012:335: de bas 'bad pa thams cad kyis //
NK041(di)012:336: dngos grub 'dod pas nan tan bya //
NK041(di)012:339: dkyil 'khor la sogs gang byas kyang //
NK041(di)012:340: rab gnas ye shes mi ldan na //
NK041(di)012:341: tshogs dang bri ba'i nus pa med //
NK041(di)012:344: sa la sogs la phyag rgyar byas //
NK041(di)012:345: rnam grol rim pa thob 'gyur na //
NK041(di)012:346: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK041(di)012:347: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK041(di)012:348: zhes gsungs pa nyid kyang spyir shes par bya ba yin no //
NK041(di)012:349: gnyis pa ji ltar bya ba'i cho ga la bsnyen pa dang /
NK041(di)012:350: rab gnas kyi cho ga gnyis kyi /
NK041(di)012:353: nye ba'i bsnyen pa gnyis te /
NK041(di)012:355: lan gsum gzhan gyis gsol btab pas //
NK041(di)012:357: bsnyen pa rnam gnyis mthar phyin pas //
NK041(di)012:358: zhes gsungs pa ltar rung mthun tsam song ba'i dbang du byas nas /
NK041(di)012:359: gnyis pa rab gnas kyi cho ga dngos la rgyas
NK041(di)012:360: 'bring bsdus pa'i rnam bzhag 'ga' zhig yod pa las
NK041(di)012:361: 'dir bsdus pa nyin gcig la ji ltar bya ba'i
NK041(di)012:365: rjes kyi bya ba dang gsum du gnas pa yin la /
NK041(di)012:366: dang po sbyor ba la yang yo byad kyi bshoms dang /
NK041(di)012:369: khrus bum bsgrub pa rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)012:370: rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga dngos la /
NK041(di)012:371: thog mar bgegs sbyong ba la /
NK041(di)012:372: gtor ma byin te zhi bas sbyang ba dang /
NK041(di)012:373: rdzas zhi ba dang sngags drag po ste phyed mas sbyang ba dang /
NK041(di)012:374: rdo rje'i khro bo'i snyems pas sprul pa'i pho nya
NK041(di)012:375: dang bcas pas bsdigs shing tshar gcod pa drag po'i
NK041(di)012:376: sgo nas sbyang ba rnams kyis bgegs bsal nas /
NK041(di)012:377: zan changs sogs rdzas bzhi sngags dang bcas pas mi shes pa sbyang ba dang /
NK041(di)012:378: til dang me chu'i sbyor bas sdig pa sbyang ba rnams dang /
NK041(di)012:379: de rjes khrus kyi cho ga la dman mchog gnyis su yod pa las snga ma ni /
NK041(di)012:381: tha mal pa yis byas pa yi //
NK041(di)012:382: dri ma ngan pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)012:383: zhes gsungs pa ltar sbyang gzhi de la sbyang bya
NK041(di)012:384: bzo bo la sogs pa'i mi gtsang ba'i dri ma
NK041(di)012:385: / sbyong byed bum chu la sogs pa /
NK041(di)012:386: sbyong ba po slob dpon rjes 'brang dang bcas pas /
NK041(di)012:387: sbyangs 'bras rten ye shes sems dpa'i ngo bor bsgrub rung du byed pa yin te /
NK041(di)012:388: slob ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa yis //
NK041(di)012:389: sngags kyi gtsang sbras bkru bar bya //
NK041(di)012:390: zhes pa ltar khrus chal bku mnye dril phyis khrus gsol dbyi ba rnams kyis dag par byas nas /
NK041(di)012:391: dri dang gos rgyan sri zhu'i tshul du bsgrubs pa rnams ni nyes tshogs bsal ba'i rim pa'o //
NK041(di)012:392: dngos gzhi yon tan mngon par sgrub pa'i tshul la /
NK041(di)012:393: 'dus pa chen po'i mdor gsungs pa bzhin slob dpon
NK041(di)012:394: sh+ain+tam gar+b+hasa s+aats+tsha sgrub pa'i cho gar bshad pa ltar
NK041(di)012:395: gsol ba gdab cing sems bskyed pa sngon du btang
NK041(di)012:396: nas / rten dam tshig par bskyed pa ni /
NK041(di)012:397: sa ma ya zhes pa la 'jug cing /
NK041(di)012:398: sa ma ti'i sgra 'gro ba dang 'du ba la
NK041(di)012:399: sbyor du yod pas ye shes sems dpa' gang du
NK041(di)012:400: 'du ba'i dam tshig phyag rgya yin pa'i phyir ro
NK041(di)012:403: de nas lha ru bskyed pa yang /
NK041(di)012:404: bde gshegs 'dus pa'i lhar bskyed de //
NK041(di)012:405: zhes gzhung gang la brten pa der bskyed pa dang /
NK041(di)012:406: su pra ti zhes so so'i sgras gnas bya'i rten
NK041(di)012:407: so so'i rnam pa can du bsgom par gsungs mod
NK041(di)012:408: / blo dman gyis rten mang po'i khyad par bye
NK041(di)012:409: brag phyed pa gsal thebs par dka' ba'i phyir rigs
NK041(di)012:412: gzugs sku'i rten gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK041(di)012:413: lugs ma ri mo la sogs pa //
NK041(di)012:414: spyir na rnam par snang mdzad gzhi //
NK041(di)012:415: yang na rigs bdag gang yin lha //
NK041(di)012:416: pusti glegs bam la sogs gsung //
NK041(di)012:417: mtha' yas mchog tu bsgom par bya //
NK041(di)012:418: yang na yi dam rigs gang yin //
NK041(di)012:419: rdo rje dril bu la sogs kun //
NK041(di)012:421: sku gsung thugs dang rigs lngar 'dus //
NK041(di)012:423: spyir rigs kyi bdag po rdo rje sems dpa' bsgoms
NK041(di)012:424: pas grub kyang rigs kyi sde tshan rnams 'byed pa'i
NK041(di)012:425: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK041(di)012:426: ba'i lugs bzhin cho ga gsum bskyed kyi sgo nas
NK041(di)012:427: rten dam tshig par bsgoms nas /
NK041(di)012:428: de la ye shes sems dpa' spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK041(di)012:429: lha yi dkyil 'khor rab bskyed nas //
NK041(di)012:430: ye shes dkyil 'khor dgug par bya //
NK041(di)012:432: rten de nyid ye shes sems dpa'i bdag nyid can du byas pas mchog tu bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)012:433: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis ye shes
NK041(di)012:434: pa spyan drangs mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la
NK041(di)012:436: de nyid phyag rgya bzhis dam tshig pa la dgug
NK041(di)012:437: gzhug bcing ba dang dgyes pa bskyed pas dam ye
NK041(di)012:438: chu dang 'o ma bzhin dbyer med par byas nas
NK041(di)012:439: / slar yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK041(di)012:440: thugs rdo rje gsum dang rten gyi sku gsung thugs
NK041(di)012:441: gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor rgyas btab pa las
NK041(di)012:442: 'da' bar mi byed pas rab tu gnas pa'i don
NK041(di)012:443: gyi snying po grub par byas pa yin te /
NK041(di)012:445: rgya 'di bcings pa tsam gyis ni //
NK041(di)012:446: sangs rgyas thams cad byin gyis rlob //
NK041(di)012:447: shin tu byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK041(di)012:450: de lta bu'i rten de la dbang bskur ba ni mchog gi khrus su 'gyur ba yin te /
NK041(di)012:451: a b+hi shiny+tsa zhes pa mngon par gtor ba'am /
NK041(di)012:452: chus brlan par byas pa dang dngos su dri ma dag par byed pa tsam la 'jug cing /
NK041(di)012:453: brgyud nas go 'phang gi chos thob par byed cing
NK041(di)012:454: dbang bsgyur ba'i nus pa khyad par can bskyed pa'i
NK041(di)012:458: rig pa'i dbang lnga bskur bar bya //
NK041(di)012:459: zhes sogs dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur bar gsungs pa bzhin bsgrubs pa dang /
NK041(di)012:461: rang gi snying ga'i sa bon las //
NK041(di)012:463: de rnams byon nas thugs ka nas //
NK041(di)012:464: lha mo dpag med 'thon nas ni //
NK041(di)012:465: mchod pa rol mo bum par bcas //
NK041(di)012:466: bkra shis sgra dang bcas pa yis //
NK041(di)012:467: dbang ni bskur bar bsam pa bya //
NK041(di)012:469: de ltar rten la dbang bskur bar byed pas sbyang
NK041(di)012:470: gzhi gdul bya'i phung khams skye mched la sogs pa
NK041(di)012:471: / sbyang bya 'khor ba'i gnyis snang sa bon dang bcas pa /
NK041(di)012:472: sbyong byed bum pa la sogs dbang gi rgya rtags
NK041(di)012:473: la brten nas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i byang sems
NK041(di)012:474: kyi chu rgyun gyi bdag po nam mkhar spyan drangs
NK041(di)012:475: pa'i gdan gsum tshang ba'i dbang gi lha rnams /
NK041(di)012:476: sbyangs 'bras gzung yul gyi rten dang /
NK041(di)012:477: 'dzin byed bdag gi chos nyid dang dbyer med pa
NK041(di)012:478: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel bar gnas pas
NK041(di)012:479: mchog gi gnas la sbyor ba yin te /
NK041(di)012:481: ji ltar gling bzhi'i dbang phyug gis //
NK041(di)012:482: 'khor los sgyur bar dbang bskur ba //
NK041(di)012:483: de bzhin sngags pas ngo mtshar dang //
NK041(di)012:484: bkra shis kyis ni dbang bskur ro //
NK041(di)012:485: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK041(di)012:486: de ltar dbang bskur bas go 'phang gi chos la
NK041(di)012:487: dbang thob par gyur pa de la mnga' gsol ba'i
NK041(di)012:488: phyir mchod pa dang bstod pas dgyes pa bskyed pa
NK041(di)012:490: de nas spyan sogs dbye ba ni //
NK041(di)012:492: der ni gser gyi rang bzhin gyi //
NK041(di)012:493: thur mas spyan ni dbye bar bya //
NK041(di)012:494: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyan sogs dbye bas sems can
NK041(di)012:495: rnams kyi ma rig pa'i ling thog sogs sgrib byed
NK041(di)012:496: rnams bsal nas sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes gzigs
NK041(di)012:497: pa sogs sgrib med du 'jug pa'i phyir rten ye
NK041(di)012:498: shes kyi lha dang skal pa mnyam par spyod pa'i
NK041(di)012:499: rten 'brel yang skye mched de dag la ltos te
NK041(di)012:500: yul can ye shes kyi gzigs pa yul 'dod yon
NK041(di)012:501: la spyod yul mtshungs par bya ba'i phyir dbang po'i
NK041(di)012:502: sgo rnams bsal bar byas pa'o //
NK041(di)012:505: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya yis //
NK041(di)012:506: dkyil 'khor lha de der bsgyur sam //
NK041(di)012:507: sngags dang phyag rgya se gol gyis //
NK041(di)012:508: sku gyur gdul bya'i ngo gang la //
NK041(di)012:509: gang gis 'dul ba der bsam zhing //
NK041(di)012:510: zhes gsungs pa ltar sngar rten bskyed kyi skabs rigs
NK041(di)012:511: lnga gang du bsgoms pa de skabs 'dir ji ltar
NK041(di)012:512: gnas bya'i sku gzugs dang glegs bam dang mchod rten
NK041(di)012:513: la sogs pa so so'i rnam pa gang yin pa
NK041(di)012:514: der bsgyur ba'ang de dang de'i phrin las gdul bya'i
NK041(di)012:515: yul la ji ltar 'jug pa bzhin du byed pa
NK041(di)012:516: rnams kyis yon tan mngon par bsgrub pa'i cho ga'o
NK041(di)012:517: // de ltar rten bsgrub pa bzhin du bsgyur ba de la mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK041(di)012:518: 'jig rten na rgyal bu rgyal sar dbang bskur ba
NK041(di)012:519: de la 'khor 'bangs rnams kyis phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK041(di)012:520: yo byad kyis mnga' gsol ba bzhin du 'dir yang
NK041(di)012:521: / spyir chu gnyis nyer spyod rol mo /
NK041(di)012:523: 'dod yon lnga sogs kyis mchod cing bstod pas mnga' dbul ba dang /
NK041(di)012:524: khyad par sku gsung thugs kyi rten so so dang
NK041(di)012:525: 'brel ba nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad rnams kyis
NK041(di)012:527: sbyin sreg gam ts+aa ru'i bza' ba zhes pa lha'i zas su grags pas mnga' dbul ba dang /
NK041(di)012:528: rab gnas kyi sngags dang bkra shis kyis mnga' dbul
NK041(di)012:529: ba rnams la mnga' dbul rnam pa bzhir grags pas
NK041(di)012:531: de dag ni phun tshogs spel ba'i cho ga'o //
NK041(di)012:532: de ltar rten de gdul bya'i dpal mgon du brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK041(di)012:534: 'jig rten ma stongs bar du ni //
NK041(di)012:535: sems can lus ngag sgrib sbyong phyir //
NK041(di)012:536: don mdzad chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK041(di)012:537: bzhugs par gsol ba gdab par bya //
NK041(di)012:538: zhes pa ltar 'khor ba ji srid bar rten de
NK041(di)012:539: la gnas par bzhug su gsol ba nyid kyis rab
NK041(di)012:540: gnas zhes pa'i brda dang 'brel zhing brtan par byin
NK041(di)012:542: rang gi dam tshig bzhin du rten de la gnas pa dang /
NK041(di)012:543: mi gnas pa'i dbang med par sngags dang phyag rgyas 'ching bar byed pa ste /
NK041(di)012:545: 'jam dpal gsang sngags kyi chos nyid ston te /
NK041(di)012:546: des tshig gi rnam pa bstan pa na bya ba nus par 'gyur ro //
NK041(di)012:547: 'jam dpal rten pa'i chos nyid bya ba nus par gyur pa la ltos /
NK041(di)012:548: dper na gtsub stan brten nas su //
NK041(di)012:549: gtsub shing gtsubs par byas pa yis //
NK041(di)012:550: mi yi rtsol ba byas rgyu las //
NK041(di)012:551: stobs dang ldan pa'i me 'byung ngo //
NK041(di)012:552: de bzhin sngags dang phyag rgya lha //
NK041(di)012:553: gsum ni 'dus par gyur pa las //
NK041(di)012:555: byung nas yid la gang 'dod pa'i //
NK041(di)012:556: dgos pa thams cad byed par 'gyur //
NK041(di)012:559: gang zhig bcings pa tsam gyis su //
NK041(di)012:560: sdig pa kun las rnam grol zhing //
NK041(di)012:561: 'di na lus ni byin rlabs te //
NK041(di)012:562: rang gi gzugs su rnam bsgoms na //
NK041(di)012:563: sangs rgyas nyid kyang thob 'gyur na //
NK041(di)012:564: dngos grub gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
NK041(di)012:566: de dag ni phun tshogs spel bar byed pa ste dngos gzhi'i cho ga'o //
NK041(di)012:567: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga ni rim gsum las /
NK041(di)012:568: de nas mchod pa man+dala dang //
NK041(di)012:569: gtor ma rgya cher phul byas la //
NK041(di)012:570: chos kyi srung ma spyan drangs te //
NK041(di)012:571: mchod cing gtor ma phul nas ni //
NK041(di)012:572: sku la sogs pa rab gnas de'i //
NK041(di)012:573: srung mar bka' bsgo gtad par bya //
NK041(di)012:574: de nas bkra shis glu gar dang //
NK041(di)012:575: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pa yis //
NK041(di)012:576: bskor zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK041(di)012:578: yi dam dang chos skyong sogs 'jig rten las 'das pa rnams dang /
NK041(di)012:579: phyogs skyong dang 'byung po sogs 'jig rten pa rnams
NK041(di)012:580: la gtor ma so so'i cho ga bzhin tu phul
NK041(di)012:581: / rten ye shes pa'i ngo bor bsgrubs pa de
NK041(di)012:582: nyid lha dang bcas pa'i 'gro ba thams cad kyi
NK041(di)012:583: / phyag gi gnas / mchod pa'i yul /
NK041(di)012:584: bsod nams kyi zhing du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)012:585: srung zhing mchod pa po mi snang ba lha la gtod pa dang /
NK041(di)012:586: snang ba mi la gtod pa gnyis las /
NK041(di)012:588: rgyal ba'i bstan pa'i bka' srung mthu stobs kyi dbang
NK041(di)012:589: phyug chos skyong ba'i srung ma rgyal po chen po
NK041(di)012:590: rnam thos sras la mchod gtor phul /
NK041(di)012:591: mthun skyed dam tshig bsgrags nas rten 'di nyid phyi
NK041(di)012:592: ma'i mu mthar thug gi bar du bsrung zhing skyong
NK041(di)012:593: bar mdzod ces gnyer du gtad cing /
NK041(di)012:594: de nas gong gi gnas byed rtsa ba'i lha tshogs
NK041(di)012:595: rnams la mchod cing bstod nas rten srung zhing skyong
NK041(di)012:596: bar gsol ba 'debs pa dang nongs pa 'chag pa
NK041(di)012:597: sogs song grub / da res 'dir snang ba mi
NK041(di)012:598: la gtod pa yon bdag bsgo ba zhes bya ba
NK041(di)012:599: de'i skabs su babs pa yin te /
NK041(di)012:601: yon bdag mdun du bkug nas ni //
NK041(di)012:602: rab gnas lha la mchod pa yi //
NK041(di)012:603: rjes su gnang ba sbyin par bya //
NK041(di)012:605: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK041(di)012:606: khyed kyis nga la gsol btab pa'i //
NK041(di)012:608: ci 'byor pa'i mchod pa rgyun mi chad par gyis shig /
NK041(di)012:609: ces bsgos pa bzhin du khyed kyis kyang dang du
NK041(di)012:610: blangs pa'i tshul du 'di ltar bshams pa'i mchod pa
NK041(di)012:611: 'dis mtshon te lus longs spyod dus gsum dge tshogs
NK041(di)012:612: dang bcas pa phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i sprin
NK041(di)012:613: rab 'byams su spel ba 'dus pa'i tshogs dang lhan
NK041(di)012:614: cig pas zhal bsro'i tshul du 'bul bar mdzod /
NK041(di)012:615: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK041(di)012:617: de ltar zhal bsro'i mchod pa phul nas bkra shis pa'i stan la 'khod pa'i mos pa mdzod //
NK041(di)012:618: bkra shis la bar du gcod pa'i bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK041(di)012:620: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK041(di)012:621: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK041(di)012:622: sogs kyi mthar / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs
NK041(di)012:623: kyis rab tu gnas pa legs par byas pa'i rten
NK041(di)012:624: dang sbyin pa'i bdag po 'khor dang bcas pa bkra
NK041(di)012:625: shis par byed pa la bar du gcod pa'i gdon
NK041(di)012:626: bgegs thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du dengs
NK041(di)012:627: shig sogs drags sngags spos rol tsham rngams kyis bskrad
NK041(di)012:628: sogs kyi mthar / nas / yon bdag las sngags dang bum chus bsang nas /
NK041(di)012:629: stong pa'i ngang las sbyin pa'i bdag po bcom ldan
NK041(di)012:630: 'das rdo rje sems dpa' 'am skabs su babs pa'i
NK041(di)012:631: lhar bskyed nas / bkra shis kyi rdzas rnams bsang sbyang /
NK041(di)012:632: stong pa'i ngang las m+aam las byung ba'i grub pa'i
NK041(di)012:633: bkra shis kyi rdzas brgyad sogs rang rang gi byed
NK041(di)012:634: las phun sum tshogs pa'i dngos po thams cad sgrub
NK041(di)012:635: pa'i mthu dang ldan par bsams nas me long thogs
NK041(di)012:636: te / sngon yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK041(di)012:637: sh+aakya thub pa la gzugs kyi lha mo 'od 'chang
NK041(di)012:638: mas me long phul ba bkra shis pa'i rdzas su
NK041(di)012:639: byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du deng 'dir yang
NK041(di)012:640: rab tu gnas pa legs par byas pa'i rten 'di
NK041(di)012:641: dang bdag dang sbyin pa'i bdag pos thog drangs sems
NK041(di)012:642: can thams cad me long gi rdzas la brten nas
NK041(di)012:643: shin tu dge zhing bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK041(di)012:644: me long ye shes rgya mtsho chen po ste /
NK041(di)012:647: glang po che sa srung gis sman gi wam /
NK041(di)012:648: zhing pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas zho /
NK041(di)012:649: bram ze kun+da l+ais r+ts+wa d+aurba /
NK041(di)012:650: shing gi lha mos shing thog bilba /
NK041(di)012:651: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis dung g.yas su 'khyil ba /
NK041(di)012:652: sa yi lha mo brtan mas li khri /
NK041(di)012:653: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes yungs kar
NK041(di)012:654: phul ba sogs kyi gtong thun gyi mthar mthun 'gyur
NK041(di)012:655: dang / tshigs bcad so so'i mthar rol mo dang
NK041(di)012:656: bcas pas me tog 'thor zhing rdzas rnams rten la
NK041(di)012:657: 'bul tshul byas nas der 'khod thams cad la reg
NK041(di)012:659: de bzhin du rin chen bdun yang gtod par spro na /
NK041(di)012:660: gang yang bsod nams chen po'i dpal dang ldan pa'i
NK041(di)012:661: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po gang du byung ba
NK041(di)012:662: na de nyid phyogs thams cad las rnam par rgyal
NK041(di)012:663: ba'i go 'phang la dbang bskur ba'i yo byad thun
NK041(di)012:664: mong ma yin pa ni rin po che sna bdun
NK041(di)012:665: yin la / de yang 'khor lo la sogs pa
NK041(di)012:666: bdun re re la yang rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i
NK041(di)012:668: rdzu 'phrul gyi yon tan bdun dang /
NK041(di)012:669: byang chub kyi yan lag gi yon tan bdun dang /
NK041(di)012:670: chos kyi yon tan bdun rnams dang ldan te /
NK041(di)012:671: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa'i dge legs chen po'i
NK041(di)012:672: dpal gyis deng 'dir yang rab tu gnas pa legs
NK041(di)012:673: par byas pa'i rten 'di dang bdag dang sbyin pa'i
NK041(di)012:674: bdag pos thog drangs sems can thams cad rin po
NK041(di)012:675: che sna bdun gyi rdzas la brten nas shin tu
NK041(di)012:676: dge zhing bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK041(di)012:678: lha rdzas las byas lte ba shin tu zlum //
NK041(di)012:679: zhes sogs tshigs su bcad pa rol mo'i skra dang
NK041(di)012:680: bcas pas phyogs dus kun tu bkra shis par bya'o
